verbose_text: Were PI5P4Kgamma to be expressed at a level similar to that of PI5P4Kalpha, it would only be metabolizing PtdIns5P at approximately less than 1 molecule / cell per s, which, taken together with an estimate of approximately 500000 PtdIns5P molecules per cell could be argued to support the idea of PI4P5Kgamma having a natural substrate other than that lipid.
